title: Cheilea cicatricosa
text: Cheilea cicatricosa is a <a href="species">species</a> of small limpet-like <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a <a href="marine%20%28ocean%29">marine</a> <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Hipponicidae">Hipponicidae</a>, the hoof snails.
